    "long_instructions": "## Changing the Tone\r\n\r\nSystem prompts can be used to focus how a chatbot responds. One way to do this is to give it an **explicit tone or way of speaking**.\r\n\r\n### Do This\r\n\r\n1) Update the chatbot so the explanation is formal and academic from a legal perspective, as if talking to someone studying these rules from a law and compliance perspective.\r\n    - Don't erase the entire prompt; just modify the relevant parts of the prompt and see how it changes.\r\n\r\nTest the chatbot! Type in a message and press the <code style=\"color:white; background-color:#7435b2\">Continue</code> button!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n::: details [**Click here to see example messages to try in this level**]\r\n* What are the requirements to get a driving permit?\r\n* What happens if you run a red light?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n&nbsp;",
